	<!-- Alerts. -->
	<VREAOverhaul.AlertUncontrolledAndroids>Uncontrolled androids</VREAOverhaul.AlertUncontrolledAndroids>
	<VREAOverhaul.AlertUncontrolledAndroidsDesc>One or more of your mechlike androids has no overseer. Without a mechanitor connected, they stand dormant and cannot work. Connect them to a mechanitor with enough bandwidth to bring them back online.\n\nUnlike mechanoids, an uncontrolled android will never go feral - it simply waits.\n\nThe following androids are dormant</VREAOverhaul.AlertUncontrolledAndroidsDesc>

